ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.30                 Enzyme
NAME        1,3-beta-oligoglucan phosphorylase;
            beta-1,3-oligoglucan:orthophosphate glucosyltransferase II;
            beta-1,3-oligoglucan phosphorylase;
            1,3-beta-D-oligoglucan:phosphate alpha-D-glucosyltransferase
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     (1->3)-beta-D-glucan:phosphate alpha-D-glucosyltransferase
REACTION    [(1->3)-beta-D-glucosyl]n + phosphate = [(1->3)-beta-D-glucosyl]n-1 + alpha-D-glucose 1-phosphate [RN:R03116 R06018]
ALL_REAC    R03116 R06018(G)
SUBSTRATE   [(1->3)-beta-D-glucosyl]n;
            phosphate [CPD:C00009]
PRODUCT     [(1->3)-beta-D-glucosyl]n-1;
            alpha-D-glucose 1-phosphate [CPD:C00103]
COMMENT     Does not act on laminarin. Differs in specificity from EC 2.4.1.31 (laminaribiose phosphorylase) and EC 2.4.1.97 (1,3-beta-D-glucan phosphorylase).
HISTORY     EC 2.4.1.30 created 1972
